            <p>Adobe Inc. is a multinational computer software company headquartered in San Jose, California. The company is known for its creativity and multimedia software products, including Photoshop, Illustrator, Acrobat, and Creative Cloud. Adobe's software is widely used by professionals and individuals worldwide for graphic design, video editing, web development, and more.</p>
